'''細菌外膜'''是構成[[革蘭氏陰性菌|革蘭氏陰性菌]]的結構之一。其組成與細胞膜截然不同，比如說，許多革蘭氏陰性菌外膜的外小葉都含有脂質部分充當[[內毒素|內毒素]]的[[脂多醣|脂多醣]]。此外，還有一些細菌比如[[大腸桿菌|大腸桿菌]]的外膜經由{{link-en|博朗脂蛋白|Braun's lipoprotein}}與其[[肽聚糖|肽聚糖]]相連。

在細菌外膜中，可以找到{{link-en|孔道蛋白|Porin (protein)}}這一成分<ref name="pmid1652557">{{cite journal |author=van der Ley P, Heckels JE, Virji M, Hoogerhout P, Poolman JT |title=Topology of outer membrane porins in pathogenic Neisseria spp |journal=Infection and immunity |volume=59 |issue=9 |pages=2963–71 |date=September 1991 |pmid=1652557 |pmc=258120 |doi= |url=http://iai.asm.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=1652557 |access-date=2014-10-02 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212152608/http://iai.asm.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=1652557 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==臨床意義==
如果[[脂質A|脂質A]]（[[脂多糖|脂多糖]]的一部分）進入血液循環系統的話，那麼它就會激活[[TLR4|TLR4]]，從而引發中毒反應。脂質A很具有很高的免疫原性，並且能誘發免疫系統的攻擊性反應。這會導致患者出現發高燒、呼吸急促、血壓降低等症狀，並能誘發可致命的{{link-en|內毒素休克|Toxic shock syndrome}}。在培養中，細菌外膜可能會脫落並作爲外膜囊泡的邊界膜。另外，細菌外膜還會參與動物組織中的{{link-en|宿主-病原體接口|Host-pathogen interface}}上革蘭氏陰性菌將其生化信號傳遞到宿主或靶細胞的過程。

==生物合成==
外膜的各個部分均是從合成部位穿越細胞膜的親水和疏水層到達細胞外的，但目前其機制和能量源尚不完全明確。[[脂質A|脂質A]]的核心部分以及[[脂多糖|O型抗原]]是在細胞膜朝向細胞質一面的膜上合成，並通過兩個獨立的運輸系統被運出細胞。其中，Wzx（RfbX）爲O型抗原的轉運蛋白，{{link-en|ABC轉運蛋白|ABC transporter}}MsbA負責將脂質A的核心部分從細胞膜的內小葉翻轉至外小葉<ref name="pmid10574995">{{cite journal | author = Feldman MF, Marolda CL, Monteiro MA, Perry MB, Parodi AJ, Valvano MA | title = The activity of a putative polyisoprenol-linked sugar translocase (Wzx) involved in Escherichia coli O antigen assembly is independent of the chemical structure of the O repeat | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 274 | issue = 49 | pages = 35129–38 |date=December 1999 | pmid = 10574995 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.274.49.35129| url = }}</ref><ref name="pmid8606190">{{cite journal | author = Liu D, Cole RA, Reeves PR | title = An O-antigen processing function for Wzx (RfbX): a promising candidate for O-unit flippase | journal = J. Bacteriol. | volume = 178 | issue = 7 | pages = 2102–7 |date=April 1996 | pmid = 8606190 | pmc = 177911 | doi = | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_1996-04_178_7/page/2102}}</ref><ref name="pmid11278265">{{cite journal | author = Doerrler WT, Reedy MC, Raetz CR | title = An Escherichia coli mutant defective in lipid export | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 276 | issue = 15 | pages = 11461–4 |date=April 2001 | pmid = 11278265 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.C100091200 | url = }}</ref><ref name="pmid8809774">{{cite journal | author = Polissi A, Georgopoulos C | title = Mutational analysis and properties of the msbA gene of Escherichia coli, coding for an essential ABC family transporter | journal = Mol. Microbiol. | volume = 20 | issue = 6 | pages = 1221–33 |date=June 1996 | pmid = 8809774 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2958.1996.tb02642.x| url =https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-microbiology_1996-06_20_6/page/1221}}</ref><ref name="pmid9575204">{{cite journal | author = Zhou Z, White KA, Polissi A, Georgopoulos C, Raetz CR | title = Function of Escherichia coli MsbA, an essential ABC family transporter, in lipid A and phospholipid biosynthesis | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 273 | issue = 20 | pages = 12466–75 |date=May 1998 | pmid = 9575204 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.273.20.12466| url = }}</ref>。隨後，O型抗原的重複單元會在[[周质空间|壁膜間隙]]中被Wzy[[聚合酶|聚合酶]]聚合，並由WaaL[[連接酶|連接酶]]將之與脂質A連接<ref name="pmid12045108">{{cite journal | author = Raetz CR, Whitfield C | title = Lipopolysaccharide endotoxins | journal = Annu. Rev. Biochem. | volume = 71 | issue = | pages = 635–700 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12045108 | pmc = 2569852 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.71.110601.135414 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-biochemistry_2002_71/page/635}}</ref><ref name="pmid18424520">{{cite journal | author = Sperandeo P, Lau FK, Carpentieri A, De Castro C, Molinaro A, Deho G, Silhavy TJ, Polissi A | title = Functional analysis of the protein machinery required for transport of lipopolysaccharide to the outer membrane of Escherichia coli | journal = J. Bacteriol. | volume = 190 | issue = 13 | pages = 4460–9 |date=July 2008 | pmid = 18424520 | pmc = 2446812 | doi = 10.1128/JB.00270-08 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2008-07_190_13/page/4460}}</ref>。

[[脂多醣|脂多醣]]的轉運物質由LptA、LptB、LptC、LptD、LptE五種[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]組成。這一事實可以由以下證據支持：在上述5種蛋白質的任一種缺乏時，都會阻斷脂多醣的組裝通路，並導致相似的外膜的生物合成受損。此外，每個[[細胞區室|細胞區室]]中這五種蛋白質中的任一一種所在的位置都揭示出了脂多醣組裝通路的機制<ref name="pmid18424520"/>。

脂多醣在從細胞膜內被轉運到細胞膜外時需要LptC的參與<ref name="pmid18424520"/>。LptE會與LptD結合爲一個複合體，這個複合體會參與脂多醣在外膜的外小葉上的組裝，它包膜合成過程中不可或缺<ref name="pmid18424520"/><ref name="pmid16861298">{{cite journal | author = Wu T, McCandlish AC, Gronenberg LS, Chng SS, Silhavy TJ, Kahne D | title = Identification of a protein complex that assembles lipopolysaccharide in the outer membrane of Escherichia coli | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 103 | issue = 31 | pages = 11754–9 |date=August 2006 | pmid = 16861298 | pmc = 1544242 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0604744103 | url = }}</ref><ref name="pmid15192148">{{cite journal | author = Bos MP, Tefsen B, Geurtsen J, Tommassen J | title = Identification of an outer membrane protein required for the transport of lipopolysaccharide to the bacterial cell surface | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 101 | issue = 25 | pages = 9417–22 |date=June 2004 | pmid = 15192148 | pmc = 438991 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0402340101 | url = }}</ref>。

